nstructions for the next capture location."]},{"code":101,"indent":1,"parameters":["",0,0,2]},{"code":401,"indent":1,"parameters":["It's shocking that I allowed them to escape when they were"]},{"code":401,"indent":1,"parameters":["so close, but I can't just stay depressed. I have to move"]},{"code":401,"indent":1,"parameters":["forward for Mai's sake!"]},{"code":230,"indent":1,"parameters":[10]},{"code":101,"indent":1,"parameters":["小田巻-三郎（スーツ）_表情一覧",6,0,2]},{"code":401,"indent":1,"parameters":["Principal"]},{"code":401,"indent":1,"parameters":["\"I was surprised by how strong Kosakai is, more than I thought. But I"]},{"code":401,"indent":1,"parameters":["can't do something silly like giving up there.\""]},{"code":101,"indent":1,"parameters":["小田巻-三郎（スーツ）_表情一覧",5,0,2]},{"code":401,"indent":1,"parameters":["Principal"]},{"code":401,"indent":1,"parameters":["\"I need to have a little more fun with various things. Muhoho.\""]},{"code":108,"indent":1,"parameters":["電話"]},{"code":251,"indent":1,"parameters":[]},{"code":250,"indent":1,"parameters":[{"name":"携帯着信01","volume":75,"pitch":100,"pan":0}]},{"code":230,"indent":1,"parameters":[120]},{"code":251,"indent":1,"parameters":[]},{"code":250,"indent":1,"parameters":[{"name":"携帯電話閉じる02","volume":90,"pitch":100,"pan":0}]},{"code":230,"indent":1,"parameters":[20]},{"code":101,"indent":1,"parameters":["小田巻-三郎（スーツ）_表情一覧",1,0,2]},{"code":401,"indent":1,"parameters":["Principal"]},{"code":401,"indent":1,"parameters":["\"Hmm. Hello, can you hear me?\""]},{"code":101,"indent":1,"parameters":["三浦-大吾（ジャージ）_表情一覧",0,0,2]},{"code":401,"indent":1,"parameters":["Miura"]},{"code":401,"indent":1,"parameters":["\"Yes, I can hear you.\""]},{"code":101,"indent":1,"parameters":["山本-勉（スーツ）_表情一覧",1,0,2]},{"code":401,"indent":1,"parameters":["Vice Principal"]},{"code":401,"indent":1,"parameters":["\"I can hear the principal's voice just fine too.\""]},{"code":101,"indent":1,"parameters":["小田巻-三郎（スーツ）_表情一覧",1,0,2]},{"code":401,"indent":1,"parameters":["Principal"]},{"code":401,"indent":1,"parameters":["\"That's good to hear. Next, I was thinking that I'd like you"]},{"code":401,"indent":1,"parameters":["two to partner with Rio Kosakai.\""]},{"code":101,"indent":1,"parameters":["三浦-大吾（ジャージ）_表情一覧",5,0,2]},{"code":401,"indent":1,"parameters":["Miura"]},{"code":401,"indent":1,"parameters":["\"Oh... Is it okay for the Vice Principal and me to handle"]},{"code":401,"indent":1,"parameters":["Kosakai together?\""]},{"code":101,"indent":1,"parameters":["山本-勉（スーツ）_表情一覧",6,0,2]},{"code":401,"indent":1,"parameters":["Vice Principal"]},{"code":401,"indent":1,"parameters":["\"If the two of us were to fight together, even Kosakai"]},{"code":401,"indent":1,"parameters":["would be in a tough situation, I suppose.\""]},{"code":101,"indent":1,"parameters":["小田巻-三郎（スーツ）_表情一覧",6,0,2]},{"code":401,"indent":1,"parameters":["Principal"]},{"code":401,"indent":1,"parameters":["\"You can do a lot of things there as a teacher--as a"]},{"code":401,"indent":1,"parameters":["clergyman, or a sex worker.\""]},{"code":101,"indent":1,"parameters":["三浦-大吾（ジャージ）_表情一覧",5,0,2]},{"code":401,"indent":1,"parameters":["Miura"]},{"code":401,"indent":1,"parameters":["\"Haha. Leave it to me. I'll make sure to show Rio the charm"]},{"code":401,"indent":1,"parameters":["of a mature man properly.\""]},{"code":101,"indent":1,"parameters":["山本-勉（スーツ）_表情一覧",5,0,2]},{"code":401,"indent":1,"parameters":["Vice Principal"]},{"code":401,"indent":1,"parameters":["\"Shall we do our best together with Mr. Miura?\""]},{"code":101,"indent":1,"parameters":["",0,0,2]},{"code":401,"indent":1,"parameters":["It seems that until now, there has only been one opponent, but this"]},{"code":401,"indent":1,"parameters":["time there will be two opponents. Can Rio, who claims to be a pervert"]},{"code":401,"indent":1,"parameters":["and a clergyman at the same time, achieve a splendid victory against"]},{"code":401,"indent":1,"parameters":["them?"]},{"code":242,"indent":1,"paramet